109typedef enum
110{
111 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_LFRC_1024 = 0x0, // LFRC
112 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTAL_16384, // XTAL / 2
113 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTAL_8192, // XTAL / 4
114 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTAL_4096, // XTAL / 8
115 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTAL_2048, // XTAL / 16
116 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTAL_1024, // XTAL / 32
117 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_RTC_1HZ = 0x10, // RTC
118 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTAL_0_015 = 0x16, // XTAL / 2097152 = 0.015625 Hz
119 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTAL_32768, // XTAL
120 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_CG_100, // ClkGen 100Hz
121 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_LFRC_512 = 0x23, // LFRC / 2 = 512 Hz
122 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_LFRC_32, // LFRC / 32 = 32 Hz
123 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_LFRC_2, // LFRC / 512 = 2 Hz
124 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_LFRC_0_03, // LFRC / 32768 = 0.03125 Hz
125 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTAL_128, // XTAL / 256 = 128 Hz
126 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTAL_4, // XTAL / 8192 = 4 Hz
127 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTAL_0_5, // XTAL / 65536 = 0.5 Hz
128 // The next 5 are Uncalibrated LFRC
129 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_ULFRC_64, // ULFRC / 16 = 64 Hz (uncal LFRC)
130 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_ULFRC_8, // ULFRC / 128 = 8 Hz (uncal LFRC)
131 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_ULFRC_1, // ULFRC / 1024 = 1 Hz (uncal LFRC)
132 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_ULFRC_0_25, // ULFRC / 4096 = 0.25 Hz (uncal LFRC)
133 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_ULFRC_0_0009, // ULFRC / 1M = 0.000976 Hz (uncal LFRC)
134 //
135 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_LFRC_0_0004 = 0x31, // LFRC / 2M = 0.00048828125 Hz
136 // Following are Not Autoenabled ("NE")
137 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTALNE_32768 = 0x35, // XTALNE / 1 = 32768 Hz
138 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_XTALNE_2048, // XTALNE / 16 = 2048 Hz
139 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_LFRCNE_32, // LFRCNE / 32 = 32 Hz
140 AM_HAL_CLKGEN_CLKOUT_LFRCNE_1024 = 0x39 // LFRCNE / 1 = 1024 Hz
141} am_hal_clkgen_clkout_e;
